  "texts": [
    "Table 12 presents a compilation of the available survey areas when masking specific bits, and combinations of bits.",
    "We note a few particular examples.",
    "First, the area of the survey when considering all available tiles after removing overlaps ('WCS', bit 14) is 1331.0 deg 2.",
    "This area is then further reduced when considering masking of artefacts, stars, stellar reflections, and missing chips in the THELI-Lens rband imaging ('WCS+THELI-Lens', bits {1-4, 14}) to 1145.4 deg 2.",
    "Considering only the area available to all of the ugri 1 i 2bands ('WCS+THELI-Lens+ASTROWISE', bits {1-8, 14}), the survey area reduces to 1074.8 deg 2."
  ],
